<text top="88" left="90" width="60" height="14" font="13"><b>S/PV.5671 </b></text>
<text top="93" left="453" width="3" height="14" font="0"> </text>
<text top="108" left="90" width="3" height="14" font="0"> </text>
<text top="1081" left="787" width="44" height="12" font="14">07-32360 </text>
<text top="1081" left="90" width="10" height="14" font="13"><b>4 </b></text>
<text top="1096" left="90" width="3" height="14" font="13"><b> </b></text>
<text top="132" left="126" width="330" height="17" font="3">General, with a view to determining whether the </text>
<text top="150" left="126" width="335" height="17" font="3">conditions are in place for deployment of a </text>
<text top="168" left="126" width="270" height="17" font="3">United Nations peacekeeping operation." </text>
<text top="195" left="90" width="7" height="17" font="3"> </text>
<text top="195" left="126" width="331" height="17" font="3">This statement will be issued as a document of </text>
<text top="213" left="90" width="386" height="17" font="3">the Security Council under the symbol </text>
<text top="231" left="90" width="117" height="17" font="3">S/PRST/2007/13. </text>
<text top="132" left="468" width="10" height="17" font="3"> </text>
<text top="132" left="504" width="334" height="17" font="3">The Security Council has thus concluded the </text>
<text top="150" left="468" width="368" height="17" font="3">present stage of its consideration of the item on its </text>
<text top="168" left="468" width="53" height="17" font="3">agenda. </text>
<text top="195" left="468" width="4" height="17" font="3"> </text>
<text top="195" left="504" width="203" height="17" font="5"><i>The meeting rose at 12.20 p.m. </i></text>
